

Hello Thank you for visiting!!
To use the web application which tells the weather of the  any country .
It is the weather application in which a user can come and know the temperature of any country.
Instructions:-

1.You have to just enter the country name, All the things will be done by the api For which we are using (openweathermap) API.
2.I have included my API So there is no need to mention it.
3.You can also convert the temperature from Fahrenheit to Celsius and Celsius to Fahrenheit For which a checkbox button is given which show what you want to do.
4.A home button and about in the navbar for more information.
5.In the website you can see five days weather forecast.
6.The weather website is fully responsive you can either open in laptop, tab, phone ( small size, large size, medium)